{"tid":1507651,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非全面重場 2/9再一次大罷工","createTime":"2019-08-26T08:49:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T09:13:04.000Z","uid":202558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"70ae5623b87ae8a276744c5b76e4f203ea9bc8d9","tid":1507651,"uid":202558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T08:49:55.000Z","msg":"新手 代朋友出post<br />\n<br />\n其實大家有冇人諗過要再嚟一次大罷工。<br />\n<br />\n有上次經驗，今次應該要國泰、地鐵、九巴、醫護、公務員、金融業全部在2/9 帶頭，其他市民嚮應。<br />\n<br />\n全港罷工市民於當日一齊到機場「接機」。人數可能眾多，大家可以早一日去。<br />\n<br />\n盡量以和平手段，不要side track 罷工焦點。勇武手足以保護，防衞為主。防內地公安，防守外圍黑警。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">不是因為見到希望而堅持<br />\n係因為堅持而見到希望</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">光復香港🇭🇰 時代革命</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2/9再一次大罷工</span></span>"},{"pid":"acf99cc1f303b5cf347fdfe9f1f53710c15ef958","tid":1507651,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T08:50:42.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  13:00 見   <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY8LrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=2576d20d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"1dedc7195c4b37c38a3c6f8b8feeb088f1bb5b2f","tid":1507651,"uid":202558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T08:52:10.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"4da044c78a5c26c7f17b3a9909a8242b82284e86","tid":1507651,"uid":7738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T08:52:46.000Z","msg":"終於有正經Post"},{"pid":"b9dc7940d9c4fb9a4eecfd0b93b1a45819b81222","tid":1507651,"uid":202558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0